[*][url=https://www.esoui.com/downloads/info1568-LibWorldMapInfoTab.html][b][COLOR="PaleGreen"]LibWorldMapInfoTab[/COLOR][/b][/url] - automatically scaled World Map tab icons if you have multiple AddOns[/list]
